Homepage: https://github.com/termuxvoid/MorphShell
Description: Sleek Termux Shell Environment with Dynamic Themes
 MorphShell provides a sophisticated Termux shell experience with
 intelligent prompts, syntax highlighting, and dynamic animated
 banners that change each session. Features enhanced terminal
 aesthetics and productivity tools for shell customization.
